Project 51 installation:
 
1. Return to Castle Wolfenstein (RTCW ) must have installed !
2. Unzip project_51.zip, copy pro51.PK3 to folder, where is RTCW installed ( probably to folder Main )
3. Run RTCW, in main menu enable console and write spdevmap pro1
4. Play!
